{"tid":2365936,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[中国赢了]美國放生阿里騰訊百度","createTime":"2021-01-14T06:32:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T07:00:27.000Z","uid":36475,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c2bf426cc50c3a46c9e52b7b64f44b7259634b84","tid":2365936,"uid":36475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/u1A5rRydmv6-9422V6J9fk4hYqY=/1134x755/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VF7KBCUYDJFWDMLO5UUYLXXPMI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fu1A5rRydmv6-9422V6J9fk4hYqY%3D%2F1134x755%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVF7KBCUYDJFWDMLO5UUYLXXPMI.jpg&h=1e1e1d0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（北美通訊）《華爾街日報》報道，美國政府權衡過三家中國科技公司騰訊﹑阿里巴巴及百度與中國軍方的關係，以及對經濟的潛在影響後，決定重新開放允許美國人投資。<br />\n<br />\n該報知情人士表示，在紐約上市的阿里巴巴和百度，以及在香港上市的騰訊，原本被列入美國國防部的禁止投資清單內。這些公司被視為支持中國軍事﹑情報和安全服務，美國投資者必須在11月之前，出售名單上任何一家公司的持股。<br />\n<br />\n雖然美國政府決定取消對這三間公司的投資禁令，但同時增加了另外9間中國企業到名單內，當中涉及超過100家子公司。過去，美國財政部官員對於制裁名單爭持不下，擔心引起股票拋售影響經濟，另一邊廂，政府高層希望對北京採取更強硬手段。直至美國時間周三早上，政府高層仍然認為只要解決行政上糾紛，就可以把這三間公司列入制裁名單內。<br />\n<br />\n事件最終由採取對華妥協路線的財長姆欽（Steven Mnuchin）獲勝。早前，姆欽曾致電紐約交易所總裁卡寧厄姆（Stacey Cunningham），對交易所重新向中國電訊公司中移動、中聯通及中電信的美國存託股票進行除牌，感到不滿。知情人士表示，新名單將提交給國會，最快於周三公布。"},{"pid":"0d213a9defd3dab5d551ffd9077220e56a0ceb8c","tid":2365936,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:34:45.000Z","msg":"Americans Won&rsquo;t Be Banned From Investing in Alibaba, Tencent and Baidu<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/americans-wont-be-banned-from-investing-in-alibaba-tencent-and-baidu-11610563890\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Famericans-wont-be-banned-from-investing-in-alibaba-tencent-and-baidu-11610563890&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuMo9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=e832e391\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/americans-wont-be-banned-from-investing-in-alibaba-tencent-and-baidu-11610563890</a>"},{"pid":"20b10112842b4e656d47ad8108efcfada5010c95","tid":2365936,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:40:34.000Z","msg":"呢幾間應該好多美國基金公司都持有<br />\n禁左好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1004d42fde39b1253dff9fb98cd61344d9c65816","tid":2365936,"uid":156913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:42:14.000Z","msg":"時與勢站在我一方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"556bb43967852a06f28ff085dc359963274bf2ca","tid":2365936,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:48:13.000Z","msg":"中國登贏了"},{"pid":"8ac5e9fdf12be71a25fc51e06bebfe3da28e6f76","tid":2365936,"uid":36475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20b10112842b4e656d47ad8108efcfada5010c95","tid":2365936,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:40:34.000Z","msg":"呢幾間應該好多美國基金公司都持有<br />\n禁左好麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T07:00:27.000Z","msg":"九間換嚟放生哩三間<br />\n但個九間又涉及百幾間子公司<br />\n點都係亂㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"0d213a9defd3dab5d551ffd9077220e56a0ceb8c","tid":2365936,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T06:34:45.000Z","msg":"Americans Won&rsquo;t Be Banned From Investing in Alibaba, Tencent and Baidu<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/americans-wont-be-banned-from-investing-in-alibaba-tencent-and-baidu-11610563890\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Famericans-wont-be-banned-from-investing-in-alibaba-tencent-and-baidu-11610563890&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuMo9o6IkP5%2